Package fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend

Interface Summary
BuilderIndexProvider An interface specifying an index provider builder.
SubIndexProvider This interface describes the behavior of a sub index provider, used by a IndexProvider.
 

Class Summary
BuilderIndexProviderImpl Standard implementation of BuilderIndexProvider.
ChemicalThread This class executes a reaction, it uses a reaction rule object and its ReactionRule.computeSelect() and ReactionRule.computeResult() functions to process to reactions.
Solution Central class of the library.
SubIndexProviderSolution This class represents a sub index provider on a solution.
SubSolution<T extends SubSolutionReagentsAccessor> This class implements SubSolutionReagentsAccessor and is part of a recursive structure constructed from SubSolution and SubSolutionElements objects.
SubSolutionElements This class implements SubSolutionReagentsAccessor, and is actually the bottom of the recursive structure formed with an overlapping of SubSolution instances.
Utils Utility class, used in all the project.
 

Enum Summary
Solution.Strategy Different strategies available for reagent selection sequence.
 

Exception Summary
ChemicalException ChemicalException is an exception that indicates an error inherent to the chemical library.
